    <!-- A propos -->
    <string name="about_whatIsIt">What is it?</string>
    <string name="about_whatIsIt_text">
        "This application is linked to the agenda of the University of Le Mans present on the ENT."
        "It allows you to have direct access to your calendar on your phone or tablet without having to connect to the ENT."
    </string>

    <string name="about_howItsWorks">How it works</string>
    <string name="about_howItsWorks_text">
        "The application will retrieve the list of courses, sorted by date, and display them. With each load the courses are cached on your device, allowing for offline use."
        "You can also add notes and personalized events (for example, an appointment). This data is also saved on your device and deleted when it expires."
    </string>

    <string name="about_who">Auteur</string>
    <string name="about_who_text">
        "My name is Jean-Charles Moussé, I am a student in the 2nd year in the Computer Science department."
        "Having been fed up with having to always connect to the ENT to see the schedule, I decided to create this application to make my life easier ;)"
        "Over time and remarks I improved it, to finally integrate all the departments of the IUT, notes and personalized events."
    </string>

